flowchart TD
    START([Append LOG entry])
    Q1{Is this domain knowledge?<br/>สูตร / ตาราง / vocab<br/>ไม่ใช่ วันที่ X ทำอะไร}
    Q2{Reuse chance สูงไหม?}
    Q3{Compact enough<br/>to inline?}

    KEEP1([keep in LOG])
    KEEP2([keep in LOG])
    KEEP3([keep in LOG<br/>+ link from ref])
    PROMOTE([✅ Promote to<br/>VOCAB / SYNTAX /<br/>QUALITY / etc.])

    START --> Q1
    Q1 -- no --> KEEP1
    Q1 -- yes --> Q2
    Q2 -- no --> KEEP2
    Q2 -- yes --> Q3
    Q3 -- no --> KEEP3
    Q3 -- yes --> PROMOTE

    style PROMOTE fill:#d4edda,stroke:#155724,stroke-width:3px
    style KEEP1 fill:#fff3cd
    style KEEP2 fill:#fff3cd
    style KEEP3 fill:#fff3cd
